image_analysis.description: A photograph taken through a doorway looking into a small kitchen or kitchenette. The kitchen features white cabinetry, a light-colored countertop, and a stainless steel dishwasher. On the counter, there is a paper towel roll, a toaster, a black electric kettle, and a microwave. A sink is visible on the left side under a window with a grid pattern. A white piece of paper with the letters 'CC' is taped to one of the upper cabinet doors. The floor is light-colored tile or laminate. The image is framed by a white doorframe in the foreground.
